<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.1">
<l>nantā viḷakkē yaḷattaṟ kariyāy naranā raṇaṉē karumā mukilpōl</l>
<l>entāyemakkē yaruḷā yeṉaniṉ ṟimaiyōr paravu miṭamet ticaiyum</l>
<l>kantā ramantē ṉicaipā ṭamāṭē kaḷivaṇ ṭumiḻaṟ ṟaniḻal tutaintu</l>
<l>mantā raniṉṟu maṇamal kunāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nāṅkūr which is always filled</l>
<l rend="indent">with the fragrance of the mantāra [trees], crowding [to give] shade,</l>
<l>As intoxicated bees murmur nearby [and] lovely honey bees sing</l>
<l rend="indent">Gandhāra melodies in all directions,</l>
<l>The place where unblinking [celestials] always worship as [they] say,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Unextinguished lamp! You who are difficult to measure!</l>
<l>Nara Nāraṇaṉ! Father who is like a great, dark cloud,</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious to us!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
